name: CATS-TC1500
comment:
CATS-TC1500 is specially designed for the requirements of highly dynamic transmission and engine test benches. The basis is a  SIMATIC S7-1518 MFP high-performance controller.
For the digital regulation and control tasks, the SIMATIC STEP7 operating system is used. 
The control system developed by Siemens contains the structures for the control of the combustion engine and load engine or the control of a 2-machine transmission test bench.

CATS-TC1500M is a specially designed closed loop control system for Test benches with up to 10 Machines. The Hardware is depending on performance request a S7 1518 MFP or an IPC 847 D with a Simatic S7 1508 soft controller.

name: MN_PSS-1560 - CP-M0375 Sentinel
comment:
The scope of this project includes but not limited to the supply of Automation system including SL150 drive to operate the GMD. 
This project is a modernization of an existing GMD application for four mills (Two Ball Mill and Two SAG Mill). The scope consists of Automation system with SL 150 drive components such as CU-320, SIMOTION D455, HMI TP900, Simatic S7-400 PLC, PCS7 software v9.1SP1, Engineering station, OS Server, Multiclients, Thin clients, ESXi server, SIMATIC field PG including softwares STEP 7, SCOUT v5.6,SIMOTION DCC, WinCC Flexible advanced and network appliances scalance (XC206). 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The entire system architecture is based on Virtualization platform with redundant servers.  Hypervisor is from VMware and Operating system based on windows server datacenter 2022 downgradable to 2019. Communication between PLC & field modules is established through

name: PC_CP-A0125- PSS-1661 - VEM GUANG XI 7135526
comment:
1x GL150 with 3x Excitation units
The scope of supply includes one start-up frequency converter GL150 and three excitation units including spare parts. The start-up frequency converter consists of GL150 with CU-320-2, scalance XB008, AOP30, IPC 127E, anybus gateway and terminal modules with air cooled converter cooling unit.
Excitation units consist of redundant DCM converter, Simatic IFP1500, scalance XB008, IPC 427E with windows firewall, anybus G/W and S7-1500 PLC. The IPC 127E is pre-installed with Windows based
Operating System, Password Protection, Malware Protection, Windows updates, Windows defender.
The connection between the converters and excitation Unit is via Optical link module (OLM). The connection to the customer control system is via Anybus-Modbus TCP.

name: OG_PSS-1654 - CP-D0054- Shell Moedijk - Turbine Replacement System
comment:
GH150 Single & parallel winding
Scope of delivery of subjected project includes Drive system of GH150 Frequency Converter for Propylene and Propylene Refrigeration which contains Sinamics CU-320-2, Scalance X005, HMI IPC277E and IQ Connect module (Option C68). 
This TRA will cover for K404 compressor single winding & K401 compressor parallel winding motor support.
Communication between Drive system & field modules are connected through Drive cliq periphery. 
Communication between Drive system & Customer DCS can be via Anybus-Modbus protocol. 
There is a ethernet connector provided in control cabinet which is locked by port blocker.

name: OG_PSS-1615 - CPD0051- MERAM Project - Starting Frequency Converter
comment:
MAXIMIZING ETHANE RECOVERY AND MONETIZATION (MERAM)
3x Starting Frequency Converters, 3x Induction Motors, 1x Starting Control Panel
Starting Frequency Converter (GH180) for Propane Gas Compressor.
Option C68 (SC500 Sidrive IQ Connector) is included. The IPC is pre-installed and complemented with whitelisting software hardening the BIOS and the installed software to prevent any unauthorized access or changes.
Connection to Customer Control System is via MODBUS TCP. Ethernet port connector on outside Cabinet door is included.

name: MT_CP-A0145 - PSS-1683 - BGH Freital Drahtblock
comment:
1x GL150 with 1x Excitation units
The scope of supply includes drive system GL150 & an excitation unit.
Drive system includes: CU320-2 DP, Scalance XB008, HMI AOP30 and IPC127 IQ Connect module, Anybus X Gateway, terminal modules with air cooled converter cooling unit.
Excitation Unit includes: Simatic S7-1500 PLC, Scalence XB008, two Sinamics DCM DC converter where one coverter act as redundant, IPC 427E, Simatic HMI IFP 1500,Anybus X gateway.
Communication between Drive system & field modules are connected through Drive cliq periphery. 
Communication between Excitation Unit & Customer DCS can be via protocol Anybus-Profibus protocol.
Communication between Drive system and the excitation unit is via Profibus protocol.
Commissioning is not in the scope of Innomotics.

name: MN_CP-M0455 - PSS-1561 - Julong
comment:
GMD TIA
The Project scope of delivery is one GMD e-house container for the SAGBall Mill. The e-house container is equipped with a water cooled Sinamics SL150, Sinamics DCM, Siprotec protection devices, S7-1500 automation controllers and Simocodes for the auxiliary drive control. Mill floor mounted touch panels e.g. TP2200. An Engineering Station with TIA, Scout and Digsi installation is used for service and engineering it is typically kept within the e-house. A PDA system which is running on the Engineering Station is used to log drive and automation signals. An engineering station for the S7-1500 (TIA Portal),  drive (Scout) and PDA  is  part of the project. The cRSP remote access and the RDP service of Microsoft Windows is used to gain access and control the  Engineering station for TIA, to the programming device and the Process Data Acquisition system in case of service / maintenance. The remote access is only available on demand and with permission of the plant operator.
